('I have had enough of you!', '', 193302, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 155165, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 37899),
('No! Now I have to rebuild those two from scratch! It seems I must take matters into my own hands.', '', 193267, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 154605, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 37899),
('', 'Your arrival proved timely, yet the battle rages on. We cannot rest until these invaders are purged from our skies.', 194939, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 154902, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 37899),
