('', 'Excellent. Hopefully, Buttons has yet to be damaged beyond repair.', 193584, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 165985, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 37899),
('', 'Thank you for freeing me! But before I leave, I must find my flute. I sense it\'s nearby.', 179531, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 154342, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 37899),
('', 'You will always... be beneath me...', 197500, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 155216, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 37899),
