('', 'Dear guests and vile intruders, take your places for the dance macabre!', 197531, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 155205, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 37899),
('I do not share your love for these frivolities. I prefer my gatherings on the battlefield.', '', 197551, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 155257, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 37899),
