('I am tired of being used as a pawn by others. Will your \"help\" allow me to claim vengeance?', '', 202249, 0, 0, 603, 0, 0, 161592, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 37899),
('You must... be joking...', '', 198061, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 155888, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 37899),
('', 'Additional guards are en route. Ensure that their deaths are swift.', 198074, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 155893, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 37899),
('', 'More of those fools seek to hinder us. Do not allow them to interfere.', 198076, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 155895, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 37899),
