('To die is your only value!', '', 197393, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 155730, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 37899),
('These brokers are a greedy lot. Do not let such potent weapons fall into their hands!', '', 202242, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 161576, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 37899),
('Take this soul away and aid him, Accuser.', '', 202251, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 161594, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 37899),
('No! I will not be confined again!', '', 198072, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 155876, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 37899),
